See the
.B \-A
.RB "(" "\-\-api\-parameters=" ")"
option for details.
.TP
\fBBRLTTY_ATTRIBUTES_TABLE=\fItable\fR
The attributes table.
See the
.B \-a
.RB "(" "\-\-attributes\-table=" ")"
option for details.
.TP
\fBBRLTTY_BRAILLE_DEVICE=\fIdevice\fB,\fR...
