.TP
\fBBRLTTY_PREFERENCES_FILE=\fIfile\fR
The preferences file.
See the
.B \-F
.RB "(" "\-\-preferences\-file=" ")"
option for details.
.TP
\fBBRLTTY_RELEASE_DEVICE=on\fR|\fBoff\fR
Release the device to which the braille display is connected
