.RB "(" "\-\-speech\-input=" ")"
option for details.
.TP
\fBspeech\-parameters \fR[\fIdriver\fB:\fR]\fIname\fB=\fIvalue\fB,\fR...
Parameters for the speech synthesizer driver.
See the
.B \-S
.RB "(" "\-\-speech\-parameters=" ")"
option for details.
.TP
\fBtext\-table \fItable\fR
The text table.
See the
